Klasse TLB

edu.kit.unwwi.checkpoints.qemu.models.memory.TLB
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
Serializable
public class TLB extends Object implements Serializable
A class representing a TLB able to convert addresses from the guest memory space to the QEMU-internal memory space.
